&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manually operated valve that can be used to prevent accidents caused by residual pressure in pneumatic lines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possible to verify the supply and exhaust status of air flow at a glance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When in the exhaust position, the valve can be padlock secured. This prevents accidental start-ups while personnel are cleaning or servicing equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Push knob and then turn.&#xa0; This 2-step action prevents malfunctions.&lt;/li&gt;
